nprover-community/batteries/blob/0a7a0cdc42f531e02361cb303b8cbf0e7d334f82/Batteries/Data/List/Interleave.lean#L41-L42"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/List/Interleave.html#List.nil_interleave\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">nil_interleave</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">l₂</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.nil\">[</a><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.nil\">]</a>.<a href=\"./Batteries/Data/List/Interleave.html#List.interleave\">interleave</a></span> <span class=\"fn\">l₂</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\">l₂</span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/List/Interleave.html#List.nil_interleave","kind":"theorem","line":38,"name":"List.nil_interleave","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/0a7a0cdc42f531e02361cb303b8cbf0e7d334f82/Batteries/Data/List/Interleave.lean#L38-L39"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Data/List/Interleave.html#List.interleave\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">interleave</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Interleave two lists `l₁` and `l₂`, starting with an element of `l₁`.\n\nThis operation fully interleave the two lists when the length of `l₁` is either the length of `l₂`\nor one more. If one of the lists runs out early, the remainder of the other list is kept without\nfurther interleaving, so that `l₁.interleave l₂` is always a permutation of `l₁ ++ l₂`.\nSee `interleave_perm_append`.\n\n```\n#eval interleave [0, 2, 4] [1] -- [0, 1, 2, 4] -- The second list is too short\n#eval interleave [0, 2, 4] [1, 3] -- [0, 1, 2, 3, 4]\n#eval interleave [0, 2] [1, 3] -- [0, 1, 2, 3]\n#eval interleave [0] [1, 3] -- [0, 1, 3] -- The first list is too short\n```\n","docLink":"./Batteries/Data/List/Interleave.html#List.interleave","kind":"def","line":18,"name":"List.interleave","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/0a7a0cdc42f531e02361cb303b8cbf0e7d334f82/Batteries/Data/List/Interleave.lean#L18-L36"}}],"imports":["Init"],"instances":[],"name":"Batteries.Data.List.Interleave"}